{"tid":115960,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過獨遊德國意大利?","createTime":"2017-02-11T03:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T12:21:59.000Z","uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6c60dcfb31e877c7e1564d43cb9e6378de11b3","tid":115960,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:47:07.000Z","msg":"是咁的 想7月中自己想獨遊德國+意大利做backpacker<br />\n但係人生第一次咁做 好多野都唔識<br />\n德國同意大利香港都有3個月免簽<br />\n但會唔會到時入境又會好麻煩 <br />\n定係最好係香港搞左先呢?<br />\n食住唔係問題 Airbnb搞掂<br />\n<br />\n係入境交通先最煩 <br />\n想去Munich 同 Bologna <br />\n因為當地有朋友 <br />\n<br />\n有冇獨遊既巴打可以比啲意見<br />\n人生第一次自己去 想去盡啲<br />\n<br />\n不過而家都二月 驚機票太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962362075be2615b7b772d0f84cdc7ccb7b96a99","tid":115960,"uid":79185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:01:58.000Z","msg":"點樣係香港搞掂先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽人講德國入境好麻煩<br />\n但我果陣本身已經係歐洲，所以唔清楚係點<br />\n<br />\netihad周不時都出歐洲平機票<br />\n不過你旺季去都應該唔係平得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e1092c8bc8133624a70c1833caee3bbb3b7efd","tid":115960,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"德國毒遊兩星期"},{"pid":"58cafbe4e38cd1311934d8bb6cc2e321d2b51af7","tid":115960,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:26:52.000Z","msg":"其實唔好會好麻煩 意大利入境問都冇問就俾我入啦<br />\n德國就係瑞士火車過去 都冇問邊境問題<br />\n前排好多歐洲三寶平機票 冇就再等等<br />\n同埋你去長過3個月 唔係有咩要搞<br />\n真係多過3個月就買左附近唔係神根國既機票就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ad899294c5441eb922e6e4b589ac89b2d30ec5","tid":115960,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:28:44.000Z","msg":"試過獨遊意大利, 玩左半個月<br />\n意大利算安全, 我未試過被人偷野, 遇過唔好既人<br />\n個兩星期玩得好開心"},{"pid":"2d43307090f393a7d4769adf1f37fdcce8568b9b","tid":115960,"uid":23751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:59:59.000Z","msg":"上年去意大利玩左10日<br />\n入境剩係問我係邊轉機同去邊到<br />\n返而回果程俾人問長問短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c16fcfd99082805965d46325ca69ef9a44c2f8","tid":115960,"uid":23751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"去意大利小心賣飛黑鬼 吉卜賽乞衣同問卷黨就得"},{"pid":"1dfa0f70ca530a24d922e378a2b88b9f885bbf9b","tid":115960,"uid":82615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:09:46.000Z","msg":"入境德國唔難 我上年仲要剩係得張機票係手 酒店都冇 過關問我去邊我照直答周圍行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e0d1e922037383f5210e55d356561fdf11a2a4","tid":115960,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:17:29.000Z","msg":"唔會去好耐其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係話落地簽證都得？"},{"pid":"837cd1c19bfb2f438fb1a399bf45b942d8c76a5e","tid":115960,"uid":82615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會去好耐其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係話落地簽證都得？</blockquote><br />\n你拎特衰就唔洗簽證添 當去日韓咁<br />\n係過關問你兩句者 只要你唔on9就入到啦"},{"pid":"c57e1230f494dd2e7f8c05d7f923e4b5a83855fd","tid":115960,"uid":82615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的 想7月中自己想獨遊德國+意大利做backpacker<br />\n但係人生第一次咁做 好多野都唔識<br />\n德國同意大利香港都有3個月免簽<br />\n但會唔會到時入境又會好麻煩 <br />\n定係最好係香港搞左先呢?<br />\n食住唔係問題 Airbnb搞掂<br />\n<br />\n係入境交通先最煩 <br />\n想去Munich 同 Bologna <br />\n因為當地有朋友 <br />\n<br />\n有冇獨遊既巴打可以比啲意見<br />\n人生第一次自己去 想去盡啲<br />\n<br />\n不過而家都二月 驚機票太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n機票最平應該都係俄航莫斯科轉機 仲平過中東三寶<br />\n交通就睇你飛邊度 法蘭克福就火車落Munich 柏林都可以搭通宵火車落去 再唔係要平既可以搭flixbus<br />\n另外munich去bologna可以搭通宵巴士 係milan轉一轉車 好似十二個鐘到"},{"pid":"7286afb1e2904efcdd97ce7a4fa9c7ce11ed93c0","tid":115960,"uid":83706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"上年11月自己去咗Berlin,Munich,Frankfurt同Rome<br />\n德國境內交通都係火車<br />\n留意翻有無特價飛<br />\n29EUR一程幾抵"},{"pid":"1e7a350a079e0d7c23bf5efb513018f9c2137c48","tid":115960,"uid":6495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T16:30:09.000Z","msg":"Munich入境 <br />\n問我會stay幾多日 會去邊 同行幾多人"},{"pid":"1f969268caa7f58d76e620b04978542a4cb39491","tid":115960,"uid":11328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T18:12:06.000Z","msg":"入境有幾麻煩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去過幾次都係有一次特別耐，不過都係3-4分鐘就過到，都係要show酒店地址比佢睇之類嘅野，同埋我passport張相太細個佢唔太認得所以搞左一陣<br />\n最快係法國，問左句就比我過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4eb75b4405e77ab810cabd0cb3b52108f52162e","tid":115960,"uid":8213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T09:53:48.000Z","msg":"我上年11月經維也納轉機去柏林<br />\n乜都冇問我喎<br />\n好快就過到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6754811a9127bb6970fa74511fd0bb86b9ea255e","tid":115960,"uid":84163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T12:21:59.000Z","msg":"之前暑假試過獨遊意大利，去左十幾日，去曬個四大城市，其實個人警覺性高啲個樣睇落窮啲都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}